data.value:
Inspired by the classic board game 'Stone Age', Scrum Age is a game where you take on the role of the product owner. Utilizing developers to work on different resources to be able to complete programs and earn points.
Developed by Team 1 for ETSU SE1: Travis Barton Markis Dearstone Mark Elwartowski David Hopland Ricky Keller Ryan Shupe
